	Function Get-HardwareHash
	{
        <#
.SYNOPSIS
Generates a Hardware Hash of the Device in Intune format.
.INPUTS
None.
.OUTPUTS
Boolean.
.NOTES
This is an internal script function and should typically not be called directly.
.LINK
#ToBeDone
.COMPONENT
Microsoft Windows WMI
.FUNCTIONALITY
